bash_key1: `terminal`, `bash`, `shell` ko hum usually ek doosre ki jagah par istemaal kar dete hai.
bash_key2: `bash` ki apni ek language hota hai, jo woh samajhta hai. Jaise yeh ek valid `bash` program hai
bash_key3: `bash` mei aap woh sab kar sakte ho jo aap `python` ya kisi aur programming language mei kar sakte ho.
bash_key4: `.bashrc` `file` mei aap `bash` mei programming kar sakte ho. Toh dekha jaye, toh aap kaafi complicated cheezein kar sakte ho `.bashrc` mei kuch bhi likh kar.
